decision_makers.name: Dave Whelan
decision_makers.notes: Appointed Rösler from Brentford in December 2013, praised his philosophy and ambition

decision_makers.name: Lutz Pfannenstiel
decision_makers.notes: Appointed Rösler to replace Friedhelm Funkel in January 2020, signed 1.5 year contract

decision_makers.name: Ilja Kaenzig
decision_makers.notes: CEO who appointed Rösler in October 2025 on contract until 2027

decision_makers.name: Dirk Dufner
decision_makers.notes: Appointed as sporting director in March 2025, involved in Rösler hiring

decision_makers.name: Marc Lettau
decision_makers.notes: Hired Rösler in January 2025 for relegation battle
